# Simple cube for unit tests
# 8 vertices, 6 quad faces → 24 unique face-verts, 12 triangles after fan triangulation

v -1.0  1.0  1.0
v -1.0 -1.0  1.0
v  1.0 -1.0  1.0
v  1.0  1.0  1.0
v -1.0  1.0 -1.0
v -1.0 -1.0 -1.0
v  1.0 -1.0 -1.0
v  1.0  1.0 -1.0

# Front face
f 1 2 3 4
# Back face
f 8 7 6 5
# Top face
f 5 1 4 8
# Bottom face
f 2 6 7 3
# Right face
f 4 3 7 8
# Left face
f 5 6 2 1
